name: Wave 2C — quantifier over a described collection
description: ```
A counting quantifier (`at least N <description>`) restricted by a
whose-clause and a per-element body lowers to a deterministic reducer over
the bound collection: filter the source once, then test the count. The
collection is fetched once (`?.asList ?? []`), never re-invoked per element.
```
tags: inform7, wave2, codegen

vocab_inline cat: ```
=== vocabulary ===
A page is a kind of thing.
A page has a summary, which is text.
A page has a status, which is text.
```

source_inline: ```
---
name: audit
parameters: pages
vocabulary: cat.merconfig
---

To audit the pages:
  if at least 2 pages whose status is "published" have a summary,
    complete with reason "ok".
```

